These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daisy, zinnia
3 different pets are kept: ferret, rat, bird
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, folk, trance
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, car, motorbike
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the fan of trance##1
2. the fan of blues is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the owner of the rat and the owner of the bird##2
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
5. the fan of trance is the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Flower         | daisy | balloon-flower   | zinnia   |
| Pet   | rat     | ferret | bird |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | blues    | folk      |
| Transport     | car     | bus      | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, raspberry, tomato
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, gospel, soul
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, train, roller
The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, gardening, traveling
1. the fan of soul is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the fan of soul##1
3. the person eating raspberry is the person driving the roller##1
4. the person eating kale is the person driving the train##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the fan of gospel and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person eating tomato is the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | raspberry  | kale     | tomato     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | soul     | blues      |
| Transport   | roller  | train | quad-bike |
| Hobby           | traveling | sudoku     | gardening       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, kale, orange
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, paramedic
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, swisher, vegafina
House: palace, colonial, victorian
1. the bartender is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
2. the palace house is between the paramedic and the vegafina-smoker##2
3. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
4. the colonial house is the person eating kale##1
5. the palace house is the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Food          | eggplant  | orange     | kale     |
| Job           | paramedic | bartender  | doctor   |
| Cigar   | aristoff  | swisher    | vegafina |
| House           | victorian     | palace | colonial |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, japanese, french
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, paramedic, scientist
3 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, guinea-pig
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, water, juice
1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the japanese is on the right of the scientist##1
3. the french is between the paramedic and the owner of the cat##2
4. the japanese is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Nationality    | russian       | french  | japanese   |
| Job     | paramedic    | scientist  | journalist |
| Pet     | chinchilla   | guinea-pig | cat        |
| Beverage   | juice | sprite     | water      |

