.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cherry, plum
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, filmmaking, photography
City: edinburgh, marseilles, miami
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, fanta
1. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
2. the person drinking cola is between the person traveling to miami and the person who's hobby is photography##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating plum##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Food          | plum    | carrot     | cherry      |
| Hobby         | cooking | filmmaking | photography |
| City   | miami  | marseilles       | edinburgh       |
| Beverage           | sprite     | cola       | fanta     |

