The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, skydiving, sudoku
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, country, d&b
3 different games are played: snooker, domino, chess
1. the person playing domino is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person who growssunflower is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the fan of country is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person playing domino##2
4. the fan of d&b is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Flower          | daffodil | daisy | sunflower    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | sudoku      | filmmaking |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | country     | d&b        |
| Game           | snooker      | chess       | domino      |

