.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, peach, radish
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, vegafina, dannemann
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, fantasy, western
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, egyptian, italian
1. the egyptian is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the vegafina-smoker is between the person eating radish and the argentine##2
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person eating peach##1
4. the argentine is on the far right##1
5. the vegafina-smoker is between the dannemann-smoker and the person watching comedy movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | radish      | peach   | artichoke |
| Cigar         | old-henry | vegafina | dannemann |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy      | western | fantasy   |
| Nationality     | italian         | egyptian  | argentine       |

