.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
3 different games are played: monopoly, mah-jongg, snooker
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, cooking, august-climbing
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, dressmaker, journalist
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, july, august
1. the journalist is on the far left##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the architect is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person playing snooker##2
5. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Game      | monopoly       | mah-jongg      | snooker      |
| Hobby         | cooking    | august-climbing | chess      |
| Job           | journalist | architect     | dressmaker |
| Birthday   | july     | august          | may       |

