.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-14::.
3 different pets are kept: snake, fish, turtle
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, salsa, ambient
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, fisherman, police-officer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, time-travel
1. the owner of the turtle is between the person watching disaster movies and the fan of ambient##2
2. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the coach##1
3. the police-officer is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
4. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the fan of funk is the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the coach is on the right of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Pet      | fish    | turtle          | snake |
| Music-Genre          | ambient | salsa           | funk        |
| Job           | fisherman | police-officer | coach         |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | time-travel    | disaster      |

