.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-16::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, singing
There 3 different types of food: kale, avocado, strawberry
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, golf, parkour
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, brazilian, dutch
1. the person eating avocado is on the right of the brazilian##1
2. the person eating strawberry is between the canadian and the person eating kale##2
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is the canadian##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| Hobby       | singing | gardening | magic-tricks |
| Food         | kale   | strawberry       | avocado        |
| Sport       | parkour | cricket   | golf         |
| Nationality   | dutch    | brazilian     | canadian         |

