.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-17::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, electronic, folk
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, german, turkish
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, february, september
City: hamburg, hannover, nizza
1. the german is between the person traveling to nizza and the egyptian##2
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
3. the fan of electronic is the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is the fan of disco##1
5. the person traveling to hamburg is the person who's birthday is in february##1
6. the egyptian is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | disco  | folk     |
| Nationality   | turkish    | german | egyptian |
| Birthday           | june        | september   | february  |
| City     | nizza      | hannover   | hamburg |

