.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk, juice
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, sports, thriller
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, folk, salsa
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, november, september
1. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person drinking water##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking water and the fan of folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Beverage           | soy-milk   | juice   | water |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | sports   | epic     |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | d&b      | salsa    |
| Birthday           | august | november | september    |

