.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, mirinda
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, zombie, horror
3 different games are played: whist, billiard, go
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, mouse, rat
1. the owner of the mouse is the person playing go##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
3. the person playing whist is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person watching musical movies##2
4. the person playing billiard is the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person drinking milk and the person playing billiard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda     | milk        |
| Movie-Genre         | zombie   | horror | musical |
| Game   | billiard        | whist       | go      |
| Pet           | rat           | goldfish    | mouse       |

