.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, spinach, strawberry
The people have 3 different jobs:  photographer, doctor, police-officer
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, snowboarding, surfing
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, drawing, reading
1. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the doctor is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person eating strawberry##1
5. the police-officer is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
6. the person who's sport is surfing is the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Food        | spinach      | raspberry | strawberry |
| Job         | doctor     | police-officer    | photographer        |
| Sport       | snowboarding | surfing   | lacrosse   |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks          | drawing     | reading       |

 